{"tha-ap407:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap407:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap407:0.3":"5 Upasivattheraapadana ","tha-ap407:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap407:1.2":"anomo nama pabbato; ","tha-ap407:1.3":"Assamo sukato mayham, ","tha-ap407:1.4":"pannasala sumapita. ","tha-ap407:2.1":"Nadi ca sandati tattha, ","tha-ap407:2.2":"supatittha manorama; ","tha-ap407:2.3":"Anupatitthe jayanti, ","tha-ap407:2.4":"padumuppalaka bahu. ","tha-ap407:3.1":"Pathina pavusa maccha, ","tha-ap407:3.2":"balaja munjarohita; ","tha-ap407:3.3":"Macchakacchapasanchanna, ","tha-ap407:3.4":"nadika sandate tada. ","tha-ap407:4.1":"Timira pupphita tattha, ","tha-ap407:4.2":"asoka khuddamalaka; ","tha-ap407:4.3":"Punnaga giripunnaga, ","tha-ap407:4.4":"sampavanti mamassamam. ","tha-ap407:5.1":"Kutaja pupphita tattha, ","tha-ap407:5.2":"tinasulavanani ca; ","tha-ap407:5.3":"Sala ca salala tattha, ","tha-ap407:5.4":"campaka pupphita bahu. ","tha-ap407:6.1":"Ajjuna atimutta ca, ","tha-ap407:6.2":"mahanama ca pupphita; ","tha-ap407:6.3":"Asana madhugandhi ca, ","tha-ap407:6.4":"pupphita te mamassame. ","tha-ap407:7.1":"Uddalaka patalika, ","tha-ap407:7.2":"yuthika ca piyanguka; ","tha-ap407:7.3":"Bimbijalakasanchanna, ","tha-ap407:7.4":"samanta addhayojanam. ","tha-ap407:8.1":"Mataggara sattaliyo, ","tha-ap407:8.2":"patali sinduvaraka; ","tha-ap407:8.3":"Ankolaka bahu tattha, ","tha-ap407:8.4":"talakutthi ca pupphita; ","tha-ap407:8.5":"Seleyyaka bahu tattha, ","tha-ap407:8.6":"pupphita mama assame. ","tha-ap407:9.1":"Etesu pupphajatesu, ","tha-ap407:9.2":"sobhanti padapa bahu; ","tha-ap407:9.3":"Samanta tena gandhena, ","tha-ap407:9.4":"vayate mama assamo. ","tha-ap407:10.1":"Haritaka amalaka, ","tha-ap407:10.2":"ambajambuvibhitaka; ","tha-ap407:10.3":"Kola bhallataka billa, ","tha-ap407:10.4":"pharusakaphalani ca. ","tha-ap407:11.1":"Tinduka ca piyala ca, ","tha-ap407:11.2":"madhuka kasumarayo; ","tha-ap407:11.3":"Labuja panasa tattha, ","tha-ap407:11.4":"kadali badariphala. ","tha-ap407:12.1":"Ambataka bahu tattha, ","tha-ap407:12.2":"vallikaraphalani ca; ","tha-ap407:12.3":"Bijapurasapariyo, ","tha-ap407:12.4":"phalita mama assame. ","tha-ap407:13.1":"Alaka isimugga ca, ","tha-ap407:13.2":"tato modaphala bahu; ","tha-ap407:13.3":"Avata pakkabharita, ","tha-ap407:13.4":"pilakkhudumbarani ca. ","tha-ap407:14.1":"Pipphali marica tattha, ","tha-ap407:14.2":"nigrodha ca kapitthana; ","tha-ap407:14.3":"Udumbaraka bahavo, ","tha-ap407:14.4":"kandupanna ca hariyo. ","tha-ap407:15.1":"Ete canne ca bahavo, ","tha-ap407:15.2":"phalita assame mama; ","tha-ap407:15.3":"Puppharukkhapi bahavo, ","tha-ap407:15.4":"pupphita mama assame. ","tha-ap407:16.1":"Aluva ca kalamba ca, ","tha-ap407:16.2":"bilali takkalani ca; ","tha-ap407:16.3":"Alaka talaka ceva, ","tha-ap407:16.4":"vijjanti assame mama. ","tha-ap407:17.1":"Assamassavidure me, ","tha-ap407:17.2":"mahajatassaro ahu; ","tha-ap407:17.3":"Acchodako sitajalo, ","tha-ap407:17.4":"supatittho manoramo. ","tha-ap407:18.1":"Padumuppala bahu tattha, ","tha-ap407:18.2":"pundarikasamayuta; ","tha-ap407:18.3":"Mandalakehi sanchanna, ","tha-ap407:18.4":"nanagandhasamerita. ","tha-ap407:19.1":"Gabbham ganhanti paduma, ","tha-ap407:19.2":"anne pupphanti kesari; ","tha-ap407:19.3":"Opupphapatta titthanti, ","tha-ap407:19.4":"padumakannika bahu. ","tha-ap407:20.1":"Madhu bhisamha savati, ","tha-ap407:20.2":"khiram sappi mulalibhi; ","tha-ap407:20.3":"Samanta tena gandhena, ","tha-ap407:20.4":"nanagandhasamerita. ","tha-ap407:21.1":"Kumuda ambagandhi ca, ","tha-ap407:21.2":"nayita dissare bahu; ","tha-ap407:21.3":"Jatassarassanukulam, ","tha-ap407:21.4":"ketaka pupphita bahu. ","tha-ap407:22.1":"Suphulla bandhujiva ca, ","tha-ap407:22.2":"setavari sugandhika; ","tha-ap407:22.3":"Kumbhila susumara ca, ","tha-ap407:22.4":"gahaka tattha jayare. ","tha-ap407:23.1":"Uggahaka ajagara, ","tha-ap407:23.2":"tattha jatassare bahu; ","tha-ap407:23.3":"Pathina pavusa maccha, ","tha-ap407:23.4":"balaja munjarohita. ","tha-ap407:24.1":"Macchakacchapasanchanna, ","tha-ap407:24.2":"atho papatakahi ca; ","tha-ap407:24.3":"Parevata ravihamsa, ","tha-ap407:24.4":"kukuttha ca nadicara. ","tha-ap407:25.1":"Dindibha cakkavaka ca, ","tha-ap407:25.2":"pampaka jivajivaka; ","tha-ap407:25.3":"Kalandaka ukkusa ca, ","tha-ap407:25.4":"senaka uddhara bahu. ","tha-ap407:26.1":"Kotthaka sukapota ca, ","tha-ap407:26.2":"tuliya camara bahu; ","tha-ap407:26.3":"Kareniyo ca tilaka, ","tha-ap407:26.4":"upajivanti tam saram. ","tha-ap407:27.1":"Siha byaggha ca dipi ca, ","tha-ap407:27.2":"acchakokataracchaka; ","tha-ap407:27.3":"Vanara kinnara ceva, ","tha-ap407:27.4":"dissanti mama assame. ","tha-ap407:28.1":"Tani gandhani ghayanto, ","tha-ap407:28.2":"bhakkhayanto phalanaham; ","tha-ap407:28.3":"Gandhodakam pivanto ca, ","tha-ap407:28.4":"vasami mama assame. ","tha-ap407:29.1":"Enimiga varaha ca, ","tha-ap407:29.2":"pasada khuddarupaka; ","tha-ap407:29.3":"Aggika jotika ceva, ","tha-ap407:29.4":"vasanti mama assame. ","tha-ap407:30.1":"Hamsa konca mayura ca, ","tha-ap407:30.2":"salikapi ca kokila; ","tha-ap407:30.3":"Majjarika bahu tattha, ","tha-ap407:30.4":"kosika potthasisaka. ","tha-ap407:31.1":"Pisaca danava ceva, ","tha-ap407:31.2":"kumbhanda rakkhasa bahu; ","tha-ap407:31.3":"Garula pannaga ceva, ","tha-ap407:31.4":"vasanti mama assame. ","tha-ap407:32.1":"Mahanubhava isayo, ","tha-ap407:32.2":"santacitta samahita; ","tha-ap407:32.3":"Kamandaludhara sabbe, ","tha-ap407:32.4":"ajinuttaravasana; ","tha-ap407:32.5":"Jatabharabharitava, ","tha-ap407:32.6":"vasanti mama assame. ","tha-ap407:33.1":"Yugamattanca pekkhanta, ","tha-ap407:33.2":"nipaka santavuttino; ","tha-ap407:33.3":"Labhalabhena santuttha, ","tha-ap407:33.4":"vasanti mama assame. ","tha-ap407:34.1":"Vakaciram dhunanta te, ","tha-ap407:34.2":"photentajinacammakam; ","tha-ap407:34.3":"Sabalehi upatthaddha, ","tha-ap407:34.4":"gacchanti ambare tada. ","tha-ap407:35.1":"Na te dakam aharanti, ","tha-ap407:35.2":"kattham va aggidarukam; ","tha-ap407:35.3":"Sayanca upasampanna, ","tha-ap407:35.4":"patihirassidam phalam. ","tha-ap407:36.1":"Lohadonim gahetvana, ","tha-ap407:36.2":"vanamajjhe vasanti te; ","tha-ap407:36.3":"Kunjarava mahanaga, ","tha-ap407:36.4":"asambhitava kesari. ","tha-ap407:37.1":"Anne gacchanti goyanam, ","tha-ap407:37.2":"anne pubbavidehakam; ","tha-ap407:37.3":"Anne ca uttarakurum, ","tha-ap407:37.4":"sakam balamavassita. ","tha-ap407:38.1":"Tato pindam aharitva, ","tha-ap407:38.2":"paribhunjanti ekato; ","tha-ap407:38.3":"Sabbesam pakkamantanam, ","tha-ap407:38.4":"uggatejana tadinam. ","tha-ap407:39.1":"Ajinacammasaddena, ","tha-ap407:39.2":"vanam saddayate tada; ","tha-ap407:39.3":"Edisa te mahavira, ","tha-ap407:39.4":"sissa uggatapa mama. ","tha-ap407:40.1":"Parivuto aham tehi, ","tha-ap407:40.2":"vasami mama assame; ","tha-ap407:40.3":"Tosita sakakammena, ","tha-ap407:40.4":"vinitapi samagata. ","tha-ap407:41.1":"Aradhayimsu mam ete, ","tha-ap407:41.2":"sakakammabhilasino; ","tha-ap407:41.3":"Silavanto ca nipaka, ","tha-ap407:41.4":"appamannasu kovida. ","tha-ap407:42.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap407:42.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap407:42.3":"Samayam samviditvana, ","tha-ap407:42.4":"upagacchi vinayako. ","tha-ap407:43.1":"Upagantvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap407:43.2":"atapi nipako muni; ","tha-ap407:43.3":"Pattam paggayha sambuddho, ","tha-ap407:43.4":"bhikkhaya mamupagami. ","tha-ap407:44.1":"Upagatam mahaviram, ","tha-ap407:44.2":"jalajuttamanayakam; ","tha-ap407:44.3":"Tinasantharam pannapetva, ","tha-ap407:44.4":"salapupphehi okirim. ","tha-ap407:45.1":"Nisadetvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap407:45.2":"hattho samviggamanaso; ","tha-ap407:45.3":"Khippam pabbatamaruyha, ","tha-ap407:45.4":"agalum aggahim aham. ","tha-ap407:46.1":"Kumbhamattam gahetvana, ","tha-ap407:46.2":"panasam devagandhikam; ","tha-ap407:46.3":"Khandhe aropayitvana, ","tha-ap407:46.4":"upagacchim vinayakam. ","tha-ap407:47.1":"Phalam buddhassa datvana, ","tha-ap407:47.2":"agalum anulimpaham; ","tha-ap407:47.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap407:47.4":"buddhasettham avandiham. ","tha-ap407:48.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap407:48.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap407:48.3":"Isimajjhe nisiditva, ","tha-ap407:48.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap407:49.1":"‘Yo me phalanca agalum, ","tha-ap407:49.2":"asananca adasi me; ","tha-ap407:49.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap407:49.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap407:50.1":"Game va yadi varanne, ","tha-ap407:50.2":"pabbharesu guhasu va; ","tha-ap407:50.3":"Imassa cittamannaya, ","tha-ap407:50.4":"nibbattissati bhojanam. ","tha-ap407:51.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap407:51.2":"upapanno ayam naro; ","tha-ap407:51.3":"Bhojanehi ca vatthehi, ","tha-ap407:51.4":"parisam tappayissati. ","tha-ap407:52.1":"Upapajjati yam yonim, ","tha-ap407:52.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap407:52.3":"Akkhobhabhogo hutvana, ","tha-ap407:52.4":"samsarissatiyam naro. ","tha-ap407:53.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap407:53.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap407:53.3":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap407:53.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap407:54.1":"Ekasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap407:54.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap407:54.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap407:54.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap407:55.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap407:55.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap407:55.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap407:55.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap407:56.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap407:56.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap407:56.3":"(…) ","tha-ap407:56.4":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap407:56.5":"viharissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap407:57.1":"Suladdhalabho laddho me, ","tha-ap407:57.2":"yoham addakkhim nayakam; ","tha-ap407:57.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap407:57.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap407:58.1":"Game va yadi varanne, ","tha-ap407:58.2":"pabbharesu guhasu va; ","tha-ap407:58.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap407:58.4":"bhojanam hoti me sada. ","tha-ap407:59.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap407:59.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap407:59.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap407:60.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap407:60.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap407:60.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap407:61.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap407:61.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap407:61.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap407:62.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upasivo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap407:63.1":"Upasivattherassapadanam pancamam. "}